[thinking] **Investigating unmap issues**
[thinking] 
[thinking] It seems that an unchanged coverage means that the unmap call for getMethod isn’t being reached. I’m thinking that RAFileNIO.close might not have un-mapped because the newStore failed and fell back to RAFile. But why did it fail? Well, RAFileNIO.enlargeFile catches Throwable, so it’s not an issue with the native/JDK, and channel.map shouldn’t fail either. But what if propNioMaxSize equals 0 for the memory database? I'll need to check how logger.open sets propNioMaxSize from properties.
